items.title: 'Teens for Zohran' co-creator celebrates 16th birthday knocking on doors for Mamdani
items.author: Associated Press
items.content:
<article>New York City's Democratic mayoral nominee Zohran Mamdani has taken the city by storm. With the election just days away, canvassers and supporters are in their final push to get New Yorkers to the polls for Mamdani and see their vision of New York become reality. (AP Video: Marissa Duhaney).

#mamdani #zohranmamdani</article>

items.content:
